OL,6,FTeachers in Scotland will walk out on
OL,7,FThursday in the first national strike
OL,8,Fover pay for nearly 40 years.
OL,10,FThe action is expected to close most
OL,11,Fschools across the country, as
OL,12,Fthousands walk out.
OL,14,FHere's everything you need to know
OL,15,Fabout why the strikes are taking place
OL,16,Fand where will be affected.
OL,18,FUnions want a pay increase of 10 per
OL,19,Fcent, but had previously only been
OL,20,Foffered 5 per cent by council umbrella
OL,21,Fbody Cosla.
